Description

  Offers various utilities for various tasks.

  * Actions <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.actions>>>

  Executes actions tasks either on the worker thread or the AWT thread. It is
intended to be a singleton instance so that all menu actions have the same
tasks and threads pool available.;

  * {{{./awtchecker.html}AWT-Checker}} <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.awtcheck>>>

  Marks a method or constructor to be checked that it is run on the AWT thread.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.colorpalette>>>

  Color palate. Iterates over the palate and returns the colors.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.comboboxhistory>>>

  Decorate a combo box as the history combo box. That is a combo box that
retains a history of added items in the model.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.components.menu>>>

  Decorates a component to open the pop-up menu if the user clicks on it.

  * {{{./editcontextmenu.html}Edit Context Menu}} <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.editcontextmenu>>>

  Basic text context menu, with the cut, copy and paste menu items.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.docks>>>

  Layouts the child windows inside and outside the working area.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.fadingpane>>>

  Layer on top of a window that can be faded away. Useful to hide temporal
changes from the user.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.filetextfield>>>

  Custom text field for a file. The FontMetrics in the paint method is
used to calculate the viewable characters for the file path.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.lists>>>

  Decorates a swing list so that the added action listeners are informed if the
user select an item. The action listeners can be informed multiple time with
the same list item, so caution must be taken.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.lockedevents>>>

  Lock listener so that the methods are not called until the listener is
unlocked.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.logpane>>>

  Uses a tree table to display messages ordered in categories.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.multichart>>>

  Displays multiple charts side by side.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.panels>>>

  Sets a gradient paint after the KDE4 Oxygen theme.

  * {{{./resourceaction.html}Resource Action}} <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.resourcesaction>>>

  Extends the Swing Action to pull the action's properties from the resources.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.spreadsheet>>>

  Spreadsheet like table.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.statusbar>>>

  Status bar for the application.

  * {{{./tables.html}Tables}} <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.tables>>>

  Data resources table models. Implements the <<<DefaultTableModel>>> to show
the application data.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.toolbarmenu>>>

  Creates a pop-up menu to set text position and icon size of the added
actions.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.tooltip>>>

  Shows an artificial tool-tip for a component. The text of the tool-tip can be
set independently of the original tool-tip.

  * <<<com.anrisoftware.prefdialog.miscswing.validatingfields>>>

  Using an input verifier to verify the input on focus lost and input enter.
Mark the field and show a tool-tip text if the input is not valid.

